event_definitions.description:
Cover the following cases:
- The Blank-API cannot connect to Blank, this could be a DNS issue (eg. full_message:"Failed to route event via endpoint:");
- Blank respond to the Blank-API TEXT=977, which means that Blank is not available to respond;
- The Blank-API reterieve an exception containing "Cannot get connection for URL", which could bean that it cannot connect to a database, eg. BTOS.
